  "description": "BeeTD is a difficult tower defence game about fighting wasps!\n\nThere is a bunch of powers to pick from, annoying wind pushing away all your insects, and much more.\n\nEach power comes with a unique set of insects, giving you lots of different playstyles to try out. Each power also comes with its own challenge to complete to unlock new insects to use!\n\nAfter you beat a boss or encounter an item wasp, you have an opportunity to pick one of the three items. Some more useful than others...\n\nSpend the energy you get over time to activate special powers for some of your bugs. Spend your energy wisely, as it takes a while to fill back up!",
  "description_short": "BeeTD is a tower defence game all about protecting yourself from summer's greatest menace. The wasp. Do not let the cute visuals fool you, for the wasps have no mercy.",
